/*************
This contains common info on tools to make it easier for us to work on
them and be on the same page.
*************/


svn
svn status - displays all files that are not in svn. Useful if you forget a 
file
svn log - logs changes
svn move - moves a file; do not use move or svn delete then try to move the
file, the file will be deleted.

imagemagick
Resize increase by 50%
convert backgroundtiles.png -resize 150% bigbackgroundtiles.png

Convert a color to transparent
convert -transparent "rgb(x,x,x)" TileMap.png TransparentTileMap.png
Note: to find the color to be made transparent. Use GIMP's "Color Picker Tool". Click on
the color then double click on the square box. Copy the RGB values in order. Red-Green-Blue
